    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated"><em>Last updated: December 2024</em></p>
    
    <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you join Job Club, we collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name and email address</li>
      <li>Major and graduation year</li>
      <li>Professional URLs (LinkedIn, GitHub, Portfolio, Calendly) - if provided</li>
      <li>Career goals and mentorship interest</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Send you a personalized onboarding checklist based on your profile</li>
      <li>Track your progress in our member management system</li>
      <li>Post your introduction to our Discord community (with your name and career goal)</li>
      <li>Send relevant event notifications and resources</li>
      <li>Match you with mentors (if you expressed interest)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following services to operate Job Club:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Sanity CMS:</strong> Stores member profiles, events, and content</li>
      <li><strong>HubSpot/Airtable:</strong> Manages member data and communications</li>
      <li><strong>Zapier/Make:</strong> Automates onboarding workflows and notifications</li>
      <li><strong>Discord:</strong> Community platform for member interaction</li>
      <li><strong>Plausible/Google Analytics:</strong> Website analytics (only with your consent)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies only with your explicit consent. Our analytics tool tracks page views and basic events to help us improve the site. You can accept or reject cookies using the banner that appears when you first visit our site.</p>
    <p>If you reject cookies, we will not track your activity, and only essential cookies (if any) will be used.</p>
    
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access</strong> your personal data we have stored</li>
      <li><strong>Correct</strong> any inaccurate information</li>
      <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data from our systems</li>
      <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> for analytics cookies at any time</li>
      <li><strong>Export</strong> your data in a portable format</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data for as long as you are an active member of Job Club. If you request deletion, we will remove your data within 30 days.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your data, including using secure connections (HTTPS) and limiting access to authorized personnel only.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Deletion Requests</h2>
    <p>To request deletion of your data, please email <a href="mailto:jobclub@njit.edu">jobclub@njit.edu</a> with "Data Deletion Request" in the subject line.</p>
    
    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes via email or a notice on our website.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions or concerns, contact us at <a href="mailto:jobclub@njit.edu">jobclub@njit.edu</a>.</p>
